.\">J.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ BJ\">BJ</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.2.5</biblScope> </bibl> ; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τὰ ἐκ π</foreign>. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">superfluities</tr_>, opp. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τὰ ἀναγκαῖα</foreign>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg044:118a:6\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Top.\">Top.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">118a6</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n81828.3\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">superiority</tr_> of numbers or force, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:71\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.71</biblScope> </bibl> ; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τοσαύτην ἔχειν π., ὥστε</foreign>. . <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0060.tlg001.perseus-grc3:4:12\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.S.\">D.S.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.12</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">π. τῆς δυνάμεως</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg2023.tlg006:5:23\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Iamb.\">Iamb.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">Myst.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.23</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"III\" id=\"n81828.4\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">survival</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τίς οὖν ἡ ταύτης π</foreign>.; what is its <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">chance of being saved?</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:gree